  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Georgia 2017</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Gruz&#xED;nsko 2017</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Cie&#x13E;om projektu je implement&#xE1;cia Smern&#xED;c E&#xDA; o vodnej politike, ktor&#xE1; umo&#x17E;n&#xED; presn&#xFA; identifik&#xE1;ciu ohrozen&#xFD;ch oblast&#xED; a tie&#x17E; prijatie nevyhnutn&#xFD;ch opatren&#xED; na zmiernenie d&#xF4;sledkov sucha v Gruz&#xED;nsku, hlavne tvorbu a vyd&#xE1;vanie v&#x10D;asn&#xFD;ch varovan&#xED; a v&#xFD;strah. K tomuto s&#xFA; potrebn&#xE9; &#xFA;daje z monitoringu ovzdu&#x161;ia, kvantity povrchovej vody a podzemnej vody a p&#xF4;dy a syst&#xE9;m hodnotenia sucha a syst&#xE9;m skor&#xE9;ho varovania. Cie&#x13E;om projektu je celkov&#xE9; zlep&#x161;enie syst&#xE9;mu monitoringu a hodnotenia sucha v podmienkach Gruz&#xED;nska a n&#xE1;vrh organiza&#x10D;nej &#x161;trukt&#xFA;ry pre mana&#x17E;mentu pri rie&#x161;en&#xED; problematiky sucha a n&#xE1;vrh skor&#xE9;ho varovn&#xE9;ho syst&#xE9;mu pre sucho v Gruz&#xED;nsku.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The aim of the project is to implement the EU Water Policy Guidelines that will allow accurate identification of endangered areas as well as the adoption of necessary measures to mitigate the effects of drought in Georgia, in particular the creation of early warnings. &#xA0;The aim of the project is to improve the overall system for monitoring and assessing drought in Georgia and to propose an organizational structure for drought management management and a draft early warning system for drought in Georgia.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
